{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/WorkspaceConfiguration\/documentation\/WorkspaceConfiguration"]]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Options related to file headers."}],"relationshipsSections":[{"type":"conformsTo","identifiers":["doc:\/\/WorkspaceConfiguration\/Se","doc:\/\/WorkspaceConfiguration\/SE"],"title":"Conforms To","kind":"relationships"}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/workspaceconfiguration\/fileheaderconfiguration"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/WorkspaceConfiguration\/documentation\/WorkspaceConfiguration\/FileHeaderConfiguration"},"topicSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/WorkspaceConfiguration\/documentation\/WorkspaceConfiguration\/FileHeaderConfiguration\/init(from:)"],"title":"Initializers"},{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/WorkspaceConfiguration\/documentation\/WorkspaceConfiguration\/FileHeaderConfiguration\/contents","doc:\/\/WorkspaceConfiguration\/documentation\/WorkspaceConfiguration\/FileHeaderConfiguration\/copyrightNotice","doc:\/\/WorkspaceConfiguration\/documentation\/WorkspaceConfiguration\/FileHeaderConfiguration\/inhalt","doc:\/\/WorkspaceConfiguration\/documentation\/WorkspaceConfiguration\/FileHeaderConfiguration\/manage","doc:\/\/WorkspaceConfiguration\/documentation\/WorkspaceConfiguration\/FileHeaderConfiguration\/urheberrechtshinweis","doc:\/\/WorkspaceConfiguration\/documentation\/WorkspaceConfiguration\/FileHeaderConfiguration\/verwalten"],"title":"Instance Properties"},{"generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/WorkspaceConfiguration\/documentation\/WorkspaceConfiguration\/FileHeaderConfiguration\/Decodable-Implementations","doc:\/\/WorkspaceConfiguration\/documentation\/WorkspaceConfiguration\/FileHeaderConfiguration\/Encodable-Implementations"],"title":"Default Implementations"}],"sections":[],"metadata":{"fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"FileHeaderConfiguration","kind":"identifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"WorkspaceConfiguration"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"FileHeaderConfiguration","kind":"identifier"}],"roleHeading":"Structure","role":"symbol","symbolKind":"struct","title":"FileHeaderConfiguration","externalID":"s:22WorkspaceConfiguration010FileHeaderB0V"},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"FileHeaderConfiguration","kind":"identifier"}],"platforms":["Linux"],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"anchor":"overview","text":"Overview","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"code":["$ workspace refresh file‐headers"],"syntax":"shell","type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A file header is a commented section at the top of each file in a project. Typical uses for file headers include:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Identifing which project the file belongs to.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Indicating copyright."}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Providing licence reminders."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"anchor":"Precise-Definition-of-a-File-Header","text":"Precise Definition of a File Header","level":3,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Because Workspace overwrites existing file headers, it is important to know how Workspace identifies them.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Workspace considers any comment that starts a file to be a file header, with the following constraints:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"A file header may be a single block comment:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["\/*"," This is a header."," This is more of the same header."," *\/","\/* This is not part of the header. *\/"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Alternatively, a file header may be a continous sequence of line comments:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["\/\/ This is a header.","\/\/ This is more of the same header.","","\/\/ This is not part of the header."],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Documentation comments are never headers.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["\/**"," This is not a header."," *\/"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"In shell scripts, the shebang line precedes the header and is not part of it.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["#!\/bin\/bash ← This is not part of the header.","","# This is a header"],"syntax":"shell","type":"codeListing"}],"kind":"content"}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"kind":"symbol","references":{"doc://WorkspaceConfiguration/documentation/WorkspaceConfiguration":{"title":"WorkspaceConfiguration","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/workspaceconfiguration","abstract":[{"text":"The root API used in configuration files.","type":"text"}],"role":"collection","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/WorkspaceConfiguration\/documentation\/WorkspaceConfiguration"},"doc://WorkspaceConfiguration/documentation/WorkspaceConfiguration/FileHeaderConfiguration/Decodable-Implementations":{"abstract":[],"title":"Decodable Implementations","identifier":"doc:\/\/WorkspaceConfiguration\/documentation\/WorkspaceConfiguration\/FileHeaderConfiguration\/Decodable-Implementations","role":"collectionGroup","kind":"article","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/workspaceconfiguration\/fileheaderconfiguration\/decodable-implementations"},"doc://WorkspaceConfiguration/Se":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/WorkspaceConfiguration\/Se","type":"unresolvable","title":"Swift.Decodable"},"doc://WorkspaceConfiguration/documentation/WorkspaceConfiguration/FileHeaderConfiguration/Encodable-Implementations":{"type":"topic","title":"Encodable Implementations","abstract":[],"kind":"article","identifier":"doc:\/\/WorkspaceConfiguration\/